Life can come at you real fast. One day I’m up and moving like everything is ok the next I’m out with a stroke . I couldn’t believe that I’m 35 and having a stroke. I remember saying that going to the hospital I’m 35 how am I having a stroke I couldn’t wrap my mind around what was happening. Things got very dark for me in that hospital week after week looking at those walls and tv and getting blood drawn all day I was like this can’t be life 😢😢. Then here comes my babies. I can’t explain exactly how I was feeling I just knew I needed to see my babies!! When they showed up and surprised me it was literally the breath of fresh air I needed. I cried so hard that night after I saw my babies!! Have to say thanks to my children’s mom. Because despite us having our differences and going through this divorce you showed up with my kids in a time of need!! Have To Thank God for Keeping Me throughout this journey . Continue to follow me as I share my health journey. Let’s eat right and let’s stop feeding these diseases by how we’re  eating 
#Holistic #Swaggytime #Baker92Strong #Blessed #highlyfavored  #Heal

Man what a year this was. In January after having a stroke at 35 I honestly didn’t know if I would make it to my 36. When I had the stroke I wasn’t supposed to be able to talk walk or move my left side, BUT GOD. Those days in the hospital got dark for me like GOD WHATS UP  u can’t do this to me? The only thing that could brighten my day was my kids. I knew I had to live for them. Im BLESSED AND HEALTHY HAPPY TO BE ABLE TO STAND TALL & CELEBRATE MY 36th LOOKING FORWARD TO MY NEXT CHAPTER OF PEACE LOVE AND HAPPINESS !!! Your looking at a walking miracle LORD KEEP DOING IT FOR ME 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾 #STROKE #strokesurvivor #SWAGGYTIME #BLESSED
